ous smokehouses and other storage buildings. "},{"stage":128.5,"statement":"Water will flood the property of Chilkat River Adventures just upstream of the Haines Highway Chilkat River bridge with some other minor flooding near mile post 14 and 25 boat launches and along Porcupine Road. Flooding will impact most backyards along the Chilkat River in Klukwan including storage sheds, smokehouses and other out buildings. Significant bank erosion is expected near the Jilkaat Kwan Cultural Heritage Center Campus Traditional Knowledge camp."},{"stage":128,"statement":"Water will begin to flow over the driveway into the property of Chilkat River Adventures just upstream of the Haines Highway Chilkat River bridge. Minor flooding may occur near mile post 14 and 25 boat launches along with minor flooding of Porcupine Road. Flooding of backyards along the Chilkat River in Klukwan will get worse."},{"stage":127.5,"statement":"Lower elevations in backyards along the Chilkat River in Klukwan will be underwater, and a river access road, smokehouses and storage sheds will flood. Bank erosion is expected to increase near Jilkaat Kwan Cultural Heritage Center Campus Traditional Knowledge camp."},{"stage":126.5,"statement":"Expect flooding of yards and bank erosion near the Jilkaat Kwan Cultural Heritage Center Campus Traditional Knowledge camp in the village of Klukwan. Water will flood lower elevations in backyards along the Chilkat River near Klukwan and start to impact some smokehouse and a river access road."},{"stage":126,"statement":"Bankfull stage. Water will begin to flood backyards along the Chilkat River in the village of Klukwan."}]},"images":{"probability":{"weekint":{"stage":"https://water.noaa.gov/resources/probabilistic/exceedance/CKTA2.SSTG.prob.weekint.gif","flow":"https://water.noaa.gov/resources/probabilistic/exceedance/CKTA2.QINE.prob.weekint.gif","volume":""},"entperiod":{"stage":"https://water.noaa.gov/resources/probabilistic/exceedance/CKTA2.SSTG.exceed.90day.gif